      <li><strong>Collision Insurance:</strong> Covers repairs or replacement costs for your vehicle in the event of a collision, regardless of fault.</li>
      <li><strong>Personal Injury Protection:</strong> Covers medical expenses and lost wages for you and your passengers in case of an accident, regardless of who is at fault.</li>
